# SlopMeter pet map  —  copy/rename this file to  pets.txt  (or just let SlopMeter create it).
# One mapping per line:   PetName = OwnerName
# Pet damage is then nested under, and folded into, the owner's total in the meter.
#
# Examples:
#   Gybez = Rude
#   Vexer = Slippy
#
# SlopMeter also auto-learns: any "My leader is <owner>" line it sees (e.g. target a
# groupmate's pet and have them use /pet leader) gets added here automatically.
